show.description: Jab You Left is a gripping story about love, betrayal, and second chances. Aditi, trapped in a broken marriage, finds herself haunted by dreams of her past lover Arjun—just as he re-enters her life after 12 years. Torn between a cheating husband and a love she never forgot, she must confront her deepest desires and painful truths.
